properties.specialtweet:
SELECT * 
FROM FLOWFILE
WHERE airlinesentiment = 'Negative'
AND friendscount > 100
properties.ourairline:
SELECT *
FROM FLOWFILE
WHERE UPPER(tweettext) like '%CLOUDERAAIR%' or
      UPPER(tweettext) like '%CLOUD%AIR%'
